// rom_lut.hex - sin(angle) * nibble lookup table, shared between
// VHDL textio and Verilog $readmemh storage methods.
//
// Layout: 32 rows of 16 entries each (row = first-quadrant angle index
// 0..31, col = unsigned nibble multiplier 0..15). Values are 9-bit
// unsigned magnitudes written as 3-hex-digit tokens (top 3 bits always
// zero). Same data as the inline literal in ROM_LUT.vhd; both methods
// must produce bit-identical outputs.
